Ethics approval and consent to participate

images was obtained from all patients. A copy of the consent form is
available for review by the Editor of this journal.
The funder had no role in study design, data collection and analysis, decision
to publish, or preparation of the manuscript. The authors declare that there
are no conflicts of interest in this study.
